-- Honda's U.S. sales rise 4.7 percent in August
-- 
-- Tue Sep 4, 2007 2:05pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/09/04/us-honda-sales-us-idUSWNAS334720070904

 

 DETROIT  (Reuters) - Honda Motor Co ( 7267.T ) on Tuesday said its U.S. sales rose 4.7 percent in August. 

 The Japanese automaker said it sold 158,342 vehicles in the United States in August, including results for its luxury Acura brand. That compared with 151,253 vehicles a year earlier. (Reporting by  Poornima Gupta )